definitions.definition: To grow beyond one's boundaries or containment , or beyond the proper size.
To grow over; (of one thing) to cause (a second thing) to become overgrown (with or by the first thing).

main_definition: ( intransitive ) To grow beyond one's boundaries or containment , or beyond the proper size.
secondary_definitions: ( transitive ) To grow over; (of one thing) to cause (a second thing) to become overgrown (with or by the first thing).
